Sure, here are five example sentences in Serbian that use the word "aktivnosti" in different forms and positions:

1. Moje *aktivnosti* danas su se sveli na čitanje knjige. (My *activities* today have been reduced to reading a book.)
2. Njegove *aktivnosti* u poslednje vreme su mi malo sumnjive. (His *activities* lately seem a little suspicious to me.)
3. Ova škola nudi mnogo dodatnih *aktivnosti* za učenike. (This school offers many additional *activities* for students.)
4. Organizacija *aktivnosti* za decu tokom letnjeg raspusta je u toku. (Organizing *activities* for children during summer break is in progress.)
5. *Aktivnosti* udruženja usmerene su ka unapređenju kvaliteta života u zajednici. (The *activities* of the association are aimed at improving the quality of life in the community.)

I hope this helps!